MID_支援_カゲロウ_ニシキ_Ａ: $t1$Wmカゲロウ|7$w0|$Wsカゲロウ|$WaLately,\nI haven't seen Nishiki around much...$k\n$Wmニシキ|3$Wsニシキ|$Wa$Eキメ,|$w0|Kagerou!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,汗|!! So it was you, Nishiki.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E通常2,|Huh? It's rare to see you so surprised...$k$pI didn't think you wouldn't\nsense my presence.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|Is something wrong?\nYou haven't been coming here lately...$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E通常,|Just been thinking about things is all.$k$pTo try and find something to help you with,\nI've been following you around,$k$pand realized that I'm probably in the way.$k$pIf that's the case, then what\nI'm doing has no meaning.$k$p$E笑,|So I was thinking of paying\nyou back in a different way.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|A different way?$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$Eキメ,|That's right. Here you go!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|!!\nTh-this is a hairpin, isn't it?$k$pAnd a comb... no matter how you look at\nthese, these don't look like something$k$pyou can find easily around here.\nSo you're giving these to me?$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E超笑,|Yep!\nKagerou has really beautiful hair,$k$pso I thought that a present like\nthis would surely make you happy.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|I see, sorry. For making you go\nthrough all the trouble, I mean.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E通常2,|No, not at all!\nIf anything, I'm the one who's sorry.$k$pWithout thinking,\nI probably got in the way a lot.$k$pI was just hanging around doing as I\nplease without thinking about how you felt.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|...If it's about that,\nthen I don't really mind.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E通常,|Eh?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|All that time, I had your\npresence accompanying me,$k$pand when I realized it was gone,\nI grew a little lonely.$k$p$E怒,|Plus, if you're nearby and\nthere's an enemy ambush,$k$pit would be to my advantage\nto have you nearby.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E超笑,|Then, that means it's okay\nfor us to keep hanging out!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|Basically, so, if I find myself in a pinch,\nI'll be counting on you.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$WaGotcha!\nThen, you'll owe me one, Kagerou!$k
MID_支援_カゲロウ_ニシキ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmカゲロウ|7$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$w0|Nishiki, come out.$k\n$Wmニシキ|3$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E通常2,|$w0|Yeees. As I thought, you can\ntell right away when I'm nearby.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|Of course. Anyway, there's\nsomething I'd like to discuss.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E通常,|What is it?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|...That time, I asked for your assistance.$k$pSaying that it was okay to be\nnearby ocassionally, and such.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E笑,|Yes, I heard it clearly.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaHowever, lately, be it morning or night,\nI can feel your presence at all times.$k$p$E苦,汗|If you're around for that long,$k$pIt'll get in the way of my missions\nlike I told you, remember!$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E苦,汗|That's right... I'm sorry.\nBut I had no choice at all.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|No choice? Why?$k\n$Wsニシキ|$WaWhen I wake up in the morning,\nor when I'm eating lunch at noon,$k$pno matter the time,\nI just can't get you out of my mind...$k$p$E怒,|Before I realized, I would find\nmyself trying to look for you.$k$p$E怒,照|It looks like I really...\nreally fell in love with you, Kagerou.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,照汗|!!\nYou... with me...$k\n$Wsニシキ|$WaYes. So, please...\nLet me watch over you.$k$p$E苦,照汗|Unless... you think I'm\ngetting in the way... then...?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|That's not... that's not it...$k$pRemember, when I couldn't\nsee you for a while,$k$pWhen you weren't nearby,\nI felt incredibly lonely.$k$p$E笑,照|And when you gave me the hairpin\nand comb, I was extremely happy...$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E通常2,照|Then...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaIt'd be nice... if you\nstayed by my side forever.$k$pThat is, if you're okay\nwith someone like me.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$Wa$E超笑,照|Of course! If we're together, there's\nnothing that can tear us apart!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaThat's right. We'll be together.$k\n$Wsニシキ|$WaYup, together! I swear!\nIt won't be moderately either! Always!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Yes, always...$k
